{"tid":946031,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"陳詠謙：詞寧願憑感覺 不要問","createTime":"2018-12-18T10:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T18:41:42.000Z","uid":194600,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eca1124c1f38e73c46f405fab5de0954748e1f1b","tid":946031,"uid":194600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T10:05:27.000Z","msg":"作曲：岑寧兒    作詞：陳詠謙<br />\n編：甯子達 / 溫奕哲<br />\n<br />\n還有兩分鐘 各位來賓<br />\n頭上會飄過 白的雲<br />\n沿途是跌下來 筆尖的塵<br />\n習慣喧嘩的人 或談心<br />\n<br />\n誰要喝杯酒 各位來賓<br />\n成熟到不快樂 不興奮<br />\n舊記憶穿心 瑣碎事多費神<br />\n習慣哀傷的人 暫時紓困<br />\n<br />\n不知道 旋律會不會撫摸傷痕<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">詞 寧願靠感覺 不要問</span></span><br />\n來臨為了甚麼 這些人<br />\n場關燈 無人過問<br />\n<br />\n還有半分鐘 各位來賓<br />\n平靜到很脫俗 很吸引<br />\n啦... 不說話的旅行<br />\n習慣孤單的人 突然很近"},{"pid":"b317185d88fd4936d46dd35880e3267ff4d4580d","tid":946031,"uid":160502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T10:18:28.000Z","msg":"太高深 唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a220f10061f7f72f8c88eb510b14f4b8126e8f5e","tid":946031,"uid":142212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T10:20:55.000Z","msg":"完全唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇過林夕個啲先知咩叫真正嘅歌詞。"},{"pid":"690d0b03589976881af7010bdccd498e24ce3aa3","tid":946031,"uid":102609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T17:41:42.000Z","msg":"求下你唔好出嚟獻世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8876c6d1927058123c62140407ef1537fd2679f1","tid":946031,"uid":202557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T17:49:47.000Z","msg":"屌 yoyo首曲唔駛要<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\"